---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Container>

    <!-- Hero + Brand Story -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mt-16 mb-32">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">Our Story</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">
          Built by a parent, <span class="text-violet-700">for every family</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Families are left to navigate fragmented systems alone — becoming researchers, schedulers, advocates, and coordinators on top of being caregivers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          Behind every appointment, assessment, and waitlist is a family trying to build the best possible path forward for their child.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          UniqueApex was born from lived experience and a simple belief: families deserve better infrastructure, not just better intentions.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img src="/climbing-family.png" alt="Family climbing illustration" class="w-full max-w-[540px]" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Founder -->
    <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-16 mb-32">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <img
            src="/headshot.jpeg"
            alt="Pelin İpek Temurcan"
            class="w-52 h-52 rounded-full object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-4 text-slate-800">Pelin İpek Temurcan</h3>
          <p class="text-violet-700 font-medium">Founder & CEO</p>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-base font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">A Message From Our Founder</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-3 text-slate-800 leading-tight">
            "Behind every waitlist is a family that needed help yesterday."
          </h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            UniqueApex was born from my own journey as a parent. Finding the right providers, navigating waitlists, and managing endless coordination across disconnected services became a full-time job.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            I built UniqueApex so families can spend less time searching and coordinating, and more time on what actually matters.
          </p>
          <p class="text-violet-700 mt-6 text-lg font-medium italic">
            Every child's journey is different. Every family deserves better support.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vision -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img src="/vision-illustration.png" alt="Vision illustration" class="w-full max-w-[500px]" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="inline-block bg-violet-100 text-violet-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Our Vision</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight mb-6">
          A world where no family navigates <span class="text-violet-700">alone</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          We envision a future where every family of a neurodivergent child has access to a connected, coordinated support system — regardless of language, location, or how overwhelmed they feel.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-32">
      <div>
        <span class="inline-block bg-violet-100 text-violet-700 text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1 rounded-full mb-6">Our Mission</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight mb-6">
          Coordination infrastructure, <span class="text-violet-700">not just a directory</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">
          UniqueApex is a support ecosystem designed to help families navigate complex care journeys with greater clarity and better coordination.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-4">
          We are starting with the most urgent pain point — connecting families with the right providers. Our long-term vision is to build a fully connected, accessible infrastructure for neurodivergent families everywhere.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <img src="/mission-illustration.png" alt="Mission illustration" class="w-full max-w-[500px]" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Name meaning -->
    <div class="mb-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">Behind The Name</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight mb-12">
          What does <span class="text-violet-700">UniqueApex</span> mean?
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-violet-50 transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
            <img src="/icon-unique.png" alt="Unique" class="w-40 h-40 mb-6" />
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-violet-700 mb-3">Unique</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">Every neurodivergent child is unique — with their own strengths, their own timeline, and their own path. There is no one-size-fits-all support system.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-violet-50 transition-all duration-200 cursor-default">
            <img src="/icon-apex.png" alt="Apex" class="w-40 h-40 mb-6" />
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-violet-700 mb-3">Apex</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">Every family is climbing toward its own version of progress, growth, and wellbeing. UniqueApex exists to make that climb less isolating.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-12 text-xl italic font-medium">"Because different journeys deserve better support."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Values -->
    <div class="mb-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-base font-semibold text-violet-700 uppercase tracking-wide">Our Values</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-3 text-slate-800">What we stand for</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-violet-200 hover:bg-violet-50 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <img src="/value-empathy.png" alt="Empathy" class="w-24 h-24 mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Empathy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Every decision we make is grounded in the real experience of parents navigating an overwhelming system.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-violet-200 hover:bg-violet-50 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <img src="/value-clarity.png" alt="Clarity" class="w-24 h-24 mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Clarity</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">We make complex systems simple so families can focus on their child — not on paperwork.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-violet-200 hover:bg-violet-50 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <img src="/value-access.png" alt="Access" class="w-24 h-24 mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Access</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">Every child deserves support regardless of language, location, or how overwhelmed their parents feel.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 hover:border-violet-200 hover:bg-violet-50 transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
          <img src="/value-community.png" alt="Community" class="w-24 h-24 mb-4" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3">Community</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed text-sm">No family navigates alone. UniqueApex connects families with each other, with experts, and with the right providers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>